  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbootUs
    AbootUs is a fragment that contains information describing the team that created this project.
    AbootUsTest  
    amount
    Fragment is meant so that the end user can select amount of pictures they want to draw.
    Category
    Fragment is meant so that the end user can select the type of pictures they want to draw.
    Dbimage
    Stores a single record from database as two values: filename and an array of tags associated with the file.
    difficulty
    Fragment is meant so that the end user select their prefered difficulty, which sets an appropriate time limit for drawing a picture.
    endScreen
    Fragment was created to clean up any garbage data that might have remained and to prompt the user to play again.
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    homeFragment
    Fragment is meant to be the start fragment.
    MainActivity
    MainActivity is our NavHost Activity, MainActivity loads Navhost, and implements every fragments Interaction Listener.
    PaintScreen
    Fragment is the place where difficulty settings, amount of pictures and the pictures themselves get loaded.
